race.comment: NOBLE DECREE (9) loves this course and distance winning two from two attempts and will have come on with that first-up run out of the way. Handles all going and can play a major role in the outcome. TAKE A PICTURE (5) returned in fine fashion with a strong Toowoomba victory and winning rider Webb sticks in the saddle. Again gets the benefit of her 3kg claim and can go back-to-back to start the preparation. ACAPPELLA SUN (10) is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley and gets in well at the weights with the claim. Can improve on recent efforts. RED DEFCON (12) wasn't too far away when resuming in Listed company and will find this task a stack easier. In the mix. CUTEPI (11) next best out of the Lees yard.
